title: Wild Rengar has appeared!
body:

It entertained your allies.

Do you wish to try again?

Yes I f*cking wish to try again.

You have chosen to drop Flame Chomper's before you die.

It was ineffective and did nothing but at least you tried!

Do you wish to try again?

You have selected yes.

You may cast Corpse flash, heal uselessly or drop flame Chomper's before you die but seeing as these have all proved ineffective, do you wish to purchase a Guardian Angel and possibly get respawn camped?


It was super effective until Rengar came back and instagibbed you again. Do you wish to uninstall?

Yes Computer I wish to uninstall seeing as I may as well afk as soon as someone picks b-ttf-ck Rengar.

replies.body: As a Rengar main it gives me great pleasure to delete salty players like you :^>

this post is too unnecessarily long for what you're trying to get across. hes an assassin. the stronger meta is that of a larger proportion of tanky champs with high cc, which is the direct counter to assassins.
Rengar got nerfed man stop complaining ._.
